{
  "stem": "22652.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And if you had asked me what I was knitting I didn't quite know what I was-- maybe a little shawl, or I learned to do gloves and socks.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we would sew, and the nun would say, oh, your stitches are too big.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "You gotta make invisible stitches.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "So I never learned to, to master the art of sewing or embroidery.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "We had some reading.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "All the books were censored by the nuns.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And the social worker sent us a couple books which I never got.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So apparently it wasn't-- it didn't pass the rules.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "At four o'clock, we had bread.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "A slice of bread.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And I think it was our last bread for the day.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And so many of us would hide the bread [SOBBING] under the pillow so we could have a little breakfast.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And sometimes, by the time you went to the bathroom or washed, that slice of bread was gone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And then, in the evening, the dinner was pretty much like lunch, two boiled potato with one or two teaspoon of jam, or replaced by a bowl of beans or noodles.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "Now, girls who were menstruating got an extra portion of noodles and-- oh.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Kids who were sick got an extra portion, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "So a lot of us wanted to be sick.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "I never got to be sick.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "I might have a cold and sneeze, but my temperature never went up.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And Lilian, she was a-- she was a troublemaker from the day go.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "She got in bed, and she moved the thermometer.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "It was a rectal thermometer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And she moved it-- you could rub it-- she moved it so high that she'd be dead by now.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the nuns caught on.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
